data.description: You can see that this home has been loved and well maintained by the current owner! Situated in a quiet cul-de-sac on a large wooded lot with fenced backyard.  Enjoy the yard from your welcoming front porch or large screened back porch. Four bedrooms each with separate baths, large family room with vaulted ceilings and fireplace, kitchen with solid cherry cabinets and breakfast nook. This home has a versatile layout that includes a primary bedroom with an attached sitting room and two secondary bedrooms with baths on the main level! Oversized bonus room/4th bedroom on second level has a full bath and access to the unfinished spacious walk-in attic. New roof, HVAC & water heater. Speaker system inside and on porch to stay. 10 foot ceilings, detailed trim work and beautiful windows create a light filled and airy home.
